{"tid":2305681,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美斯差點再現上帝之手！西媒：又複製老馬","createTime":"2020-11-30T00:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T05:52:43.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c7779a8f3415857b509a657c12248dddc8ffb23b","tid":2305681,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T00:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/11/29/d/d8a9f77ccbce590dd38fd77022182d24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F11%2F29%2Fd%2Fd8a9f77ccbce590dd38fd77022182d24.jpg&h=70290249&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/11/29/a/ae2492c76f10fb49c2584464b47bf5d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F11%2F29%2Fa%2Fae2492c76f10fb49c2584464b47bf5d7.jpg&h=694d28dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  球王馬勒當拿（Diego Maradona）於本週去世，這場巴塞與奧沙辛拿的比賽籠罩在別樣的氣氛中。美斯（Lionel Messi）在入球後脫下波衫雙手指天慶祝，將入球獻給馬勒當拿。而在此之前，他也差點以另一種方式致敬了球王。<br />\n<br />\n  美斯分球策動，艾巴（Jordi Alba）溜底線傳中，古天奴（Philippe Coutinho）和比夫韋治（Martin Braithwaite）的射門都被奧沙辛拿門將撲出，隨後球經過折射彈進了網窩。在球高高彈起的瞬間，美斯也躍起並下意識伸手夠球，但他控制住了自己，沒有拍到皮球。最終入球有效，並算在比夫韋治的頭上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  《每日體育報》表示，這是美斯對「上帝之手」的即興致敬，他差一點就再一次複製了馬勒當拿的標誌性一幕。"},{"pid":"cc69453bc08451b930a21ef9856108a146921be5","tid":2305681,"uid":59863,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T01:33:03.000Z","msg":"而家有VAR 邊咁會出到古惑"},{"pid":"8eac52e6bf8d90bc8af04db625c1bd7c289948f0","tid":2305681,"uid":61604,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"cc69453bc08451b930a21ef9856108a146921be5","tid":2305681,"uid":59863,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T01:33:03.000Z","msg":"而家有VAR 邊咁會出到古惑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T04:06:41.000Z","msg":"入左先有動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49227d8b5780b68f7ac8e6ae79170ed45c4e4ffa","tid":2305681,"uid":82889,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:21:53.000Z","msg":"致敬一次唔夠仲想黎多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5889a13468a874b6b6612ef2ff26ff94f96c3637","tid":2305681,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T06:55:24.000Z","msg":"似到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係致敬咁款"},{"pid":"31b4d241095f0132dd81e91287ba047cc9ed263f","tid":2305681,"uid":213841,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T07:27:45.000Z","msg":"學唔到老馬咁carry阿根廷拎世盃 唯有學吓佢啲小動作"},{"pid":"a213d91605f0b87e92b39eae9b62e841b578402f","tid":2305681,"uid":234945,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T07:59:14.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，跳高嗰陣隻手有反應係正常"},{"pid":"169498155146906440dfedc2f2fbb673454f2f5c","tid":2305681,"uid":132488,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31b4d241095f0132dd81e91287ba047cc9ed263f","tid":2305681,"uid":213841,"like":9,"dislike":6,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T07:27:45.000Z","msg":"學唔到老馬咁carry阿根廷拎世盃 唯有學吓佢啲小動作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T08:03:52.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"69d2f662e1d7bea39acc10f2eaf7037531d294f0","tid":2305681,"uid":203491,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T08:04:28.000Z","msg":"等佢60歲可以再致敬一次"},{"pid":"f1379dcfeca7af9ad13c5295a903b1942b12d1ff","tid":2305681,"uid":44160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69d2f662e1d7bea39acc10f2eaf7037531d294f0","tid":2305681,"uid":203491,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T08:04:28.000Z","msg":"等佢60歲可以再致敬一次"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T10:09:46.000Z","msg":"致敬心臟病發？"},{"pid":"a51dbcc7555cad6994b747bb777b24dba75a598c","tid":2305681,"uid":203491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1379dcfeca7af9ad13c5295a903b1942b12d1ff","tid":23